['Our 9" x 12" Desktop Doodle Board is both useful and beautiful, the perfect addition to any home or office. You\'re sure to be pleasantly surprised by how versatile it is! Our Glassboards are made with only the highest quality materials. Each dry erase sheet of glass is smooth to write on and resists scratches and wear from every day usage. They are designed to never stain or ghost. Dry erase markers are easy to erase, and even permanent markers come perfectly clean with a bit of rubbing alcohol. The glass is engineered specifically to protect and accent the design behind it clearly, without the greenish tint that most lower quality boards have. We use high-quality tempered glass for safety and provide brushed stainless steel flush-mount clips and mounting hardware for your convenience. Glassboard Studio is committed to making sure every customer is happy with their product. We inspect each of our products thoroughly to be sure it meets our quality standards. Each has a different design, theme, and purpose. Some of the options we provide include calendars, meal planners, vision boards, schedule boards, beautiful landscapes, scenic views, fitness charts, and more. Use these Glassboards as meaningful gifts, decor in your own home, wedding decorations, family pictures, chore charts for your kids, and more. Brighten up your home and make organization a priority with Glassboard Studio!']

The rotors are cast using the finest G3000 metallurgy with strict OE tolerances - making them a perfect, bolt-on upgrade without the need to make any modifications. Precision drill holes allow for maximum rotor cooling. This keeps your brakes temperatures down during extreme operating conditions. Rounded slots help wipe away any gas or debris - keeping a clear contact patch on the rotor surface for safe, smooth braking. Silver Zinc Dichromate plating is applied to all drilled & slotted rotors, they not only look great behind your wheels, but to help prevent rust & corrosion. Get your Power Stop’s Z23 Evolution Sport brake kit and enjoy better, noise-free braking without that nasty brake dust!']

Kotobukiya Marvel Comics ArtFX+ Hulk Statue
['From the Manufacturer', "From Kotobukiya! Marvel Comics is the next great property to get Kotobukiya's ARTFX+ statue treatment and so of course the first series is none other than the Avengers, specifically the characters as they appear in Marvel Now. For the very first Avengers ARTFX+ release. well, he's big, he's green and he's always angry. it's the HULK! Bruce Banner was a scientist studying the effects of gamma radiation when he was caught in an explosion. Rather than destroy him the energies transformed him into the massive green-skinned Hulk! The Avenger stands in a classic comic book pose, angled to the side and leaning forward with his arms outstretched. The Hulk has his leading hand open as though to taunt his enemies, though his right hand behind him is balled into a fist to deliver a mighty blow! The Hulk is fantastically detailed with intricate musculature down to his sinews and veins and the harsh grimace on his face shows off the rage he can't keep bottled up in battle. Banner's alter ego wears his traditional tattered purple pants (no Hulk would be complete without them) and his skin is expertly painted with varying shades of green. The massive Hulk stands just barely under 10 Inch tall (in the ARTFX+ 1/10th scale) on his included magnetic display base. Hulk will be joined by his fellow Avengers with upcoming releases Hawkeye, Black Widow, Captain America, Iron Man and Thor, so get him to begin your collection!"]

Matthews 40" C+ Stand w/Spring Loaded Turtle Base, Head and Arm
["The term 'Century Stand' goes back to the early days of motion picture production. Before there was artificial lighting the stages would revolve to allow for continuous overhead lighting from the sun. Large reflectors would be positioned to bounce or kick the overhead light up onto the stage and illuminate the set and actors. These reflectors were made in many sizes but it seems the most popular was the 100 inch, or 'century', sized reflector. In later years studios, grips and gaffers began to manufacture the earliest versions of what we now call C-Stands. The original C-Stands had welded bases that did not fold up or adjust, but the fact that they easily nested together made them invaluable on the stage. Century Stands, or C-Stands, are an important component in the image maker's arsenal of tools. These popular stands are available in many different configurations, lengths and finishes. The unique staggered leg design allows C-Stands to be nested and therefore be placed extremely close to one another on set. The lower leg can also be slid under many objects. In the case of the Sliding Leg C-Stands, the top leg will slide on the main riser tube, allowing its use on stairs, off curbs and even as high as placing that leg on a counter top or desk. The C+offers a removable base for the risers making disassembly for travel simple and easy without being cumbersome or having the awkwardness typical of other manufacturers. Patents applied for and pending. Fast, easy opening and closing. All Hollywood models are equipped with the sliding and come complete with head and arm. This is the newest, most innovative design for C-Stands in 30 years!"]

['Improve Your Air Quality & Purify Your Home with the 6 Pack of Crisp MERV 11 12x12x1 Air Filters.  We ensure the cleanliness and high quality air filtration with our MERV 11 12x12x1 air filters through three different methods:  •\tInnovative pleated design (making it stronger than most filters) helping prevent allergens, such as pollen, dust, pet hair, mold, auto exhaust particulates, smoke, and more from passing through. All of our filters are 100% Made in the U.S.A! With that comes strict quality control guidelines which we follow to the tee.  Besides the effectiveness of an air filter, efficiency is important as well. How well do your filters take the air from the HVAC systems and put it into the space? But our 12x12x1 MERV 11 furnace air filters are manufactured using high quality materials sourced from best in class suppliers to deliver effective and efficient air filtration.
